'''Yagai spiced dindra''' was a [[Foodstuff/Legends|dish]] served at the [[Farrimmer Cafe]].<ref name="Journal11">{{JournalCite|11|The Farrimmer Cafe}}</ref>

{{Food-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Yagai spiced dindra was mentioned in "[[The Farrimmer Cafe]]," a [[Roleplaying game|roleplaying]] source article authored by [[Jean Rabe]] and [[J. Allan Fawcett]] for use with [[West End Games]]' ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' and published in the [[November]] [[1996]] [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 11|eleventh issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'' magazine.<ref name="Journal11" />

